products.title: Gigabyte Geforce GTX 1050 Ti OC Low Profile 4GB GDDR5 128 Bit PCI-E Graphic Card (GV-N105TOC-4GL)
features: Core clock (MHz): 1442/1328 (boost/base) in OC mode and 1417/1303 (boost/base) in gaming mode
Low profile design with 167 millimeter card length
Supports up to 4 displays. Recommended system power: 300 watts
Card size- H=40 L=229 W=118 millimeter. 90 millimeter fan design
Output: Dual-link DVI-D, HDMI- 2.0b (Max resolution: 4096x2160 at 60 Hz) and DisplayPort- 1.4 1 (Max resolution: 7680x4320 at 60 Hz)
products.description: Powered by GeForce GTX 1050 Ti and integrated with 4GB GDDR5 128bit memory. Featuring low profile design with 167mm card length.
